            "id": 6020283,
            "title": "〈台幣〉出口商又繃緊神經了 飆升2.6角 逼近29.5元價位",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>今 (12) 日再度強勁升值，終場收在 29.66 元，升值 2.6 角，創 2022 年 6 月以來高，台北外匯經紀公司成交值 15.82 億美元，由於已突破前高價，市場高度關注下一個心理關卡價 29.5 元能否守住，出口商也再度繃緊神經。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020283%2Fl%2F4d1cf8bc6fcd5513a23578b9f427ea40.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">主要亞幣今日強勁升值。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>今日以 29.9 元、升值 2 分開出後，最高來到 29.625 元，升值 2.95 角，終場收在 29.66 元，全日高低價差 2.75 角。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察主要亞幣，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>收升 0.87%，而<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/krwusd\">韓元</a>也升值達 0.8% 左右，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日元</a>升逾 0.5%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/thbusd\">泰銖</a>升近 0.3%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>和星元升逾 0.1%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DXY\">美元指數</a>則下跌近 0.3%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>元大投顧說明，儘管美國本月 CPI 數據低於市場預期，但認為聯準會不太可能於 6、7 月會議提前啟動降息，原因在於，關稅效應尚未完全反映，且未來兩月通膨仍可能因延後傳導而回升，通膨預期水位仍偏高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>尤其近期就業市場數據強勁，有助於穩定經濟軟著陸預期，元大投顧認為，聯準會傾向採取觀望策略，等待通膨壓力緩解與預期回落後再行動，維持「全年降息兩碼」的預測不變，自 7 月起啟動降息的可能性仍高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
